'''Tazzwit''' <ref>https://mesmunawal.blogspot.com/2020/04/les-noms-des-insectes-en-tamazight.html</ref> nɣ '''Tizzwit''' nɣ '''Tazizwit''' nɣ '''Tizizwit''' <ref>https://tal.ircam.ma/dglai/lexieam.php</ref> (s [[Tutlayt Taɛṛabt|Tsrɣint]] : نحلة) tga yan wanaw n [[Abxxuc|ibxxucn]] ittaylaln, ttyawssan tazzwit s tikki n [[tammnt]] igan [[asafar]] i kigan n [[Tamaḍunt|tmuḍan]] n ufgan. 

==Asnmarra : ==
*Amyiwn : '''Tazzwit'''
*Asgt : '''Tizzwa'''

== Gr tamawt : ==
G kra n tmnaḍin, illa ma ittinin tazzwit nɣ tizzwit i tadggat (s unamk n المساء s tutlayt tasrɣint).

== Tizzwa d ufgan : ==
Llant tizzwa g uflla n wakal ḍaṛt 45 000 000 n usggas<ref>https://www.pollinis.org/publications/il-etait-une-fois-lancetre-des-abeilles-apparu-sur-terre-au-temps-des-dinosaures/#:~:text=Le%20plus%20ancien%20fossile%20d,la%20surface%20de%20la%20Terre.&text=Remontons%20dans%20le%20temps%20jusqu,%E2%80%93%2065%20millions%20d'ann%C3%A9es.</ref><ref>''Depuis quand ?''. France Loisirs. 1982</ref>. Zund ukan afgan, ula tizzwa qqdimnt g uflla n [[Akal|wakal]], mayad a iwdjan afgan a ifaqq mas tizzwa gant yan uɣbalu n [[Amttcu|umttcu]] d [[Asafar|usafar]], mayad af iswingm ufgan g a izzdɣ didas tizzwa. 

